```plantuml
@startuml xinsongyan_talos_pal_locomotion_slmc
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "ROS" as ROS #lightgrey {
  rectangle "Whole-Body Control\n(WBC)" as WBC #palegreen
  rectangle "Desired Capture Point\n(DCM) Controller" as DCM #lightblue
  rectangle "State Estimation" as StateEstimation #lightyellow
  rectangle "Safety Layers" as SafetyLayers #lightcoral
}

rectangle "Simulation" as Simulation #aliceblue {
  rectangle "Gazebo" as Gazebo
  rectangle "PAL Physics Simulator" as PALPhysics
}

rectangle "Test Framework" as TestFramework #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> ROS : starts locomotion controller

ROS --> WBC : load plugin\n(e.g., WbcWeightedDynamicCopTALOS)
WBC <--> DCM : obtain reference trajectory\n for walking patterns
WBC <--> StateEstimation : receive pose and velocity estimates
WBC <--> SafetyLayers : check COM position, foot contact\n and joint limits

ROS <--> Simulation : interact for virtual testing
Simulation --> Gazebo : simulate with actuator dynamics
Simulation --> PALPhysics : simulate without actuator dynamics

TestFramework --> ROS : validate locomotion controller
TestFramework --> WBC : test balancing, stepping, walking
TestFramework --> SafetyLayers : test contact monitoring

@enduml
```